=head1 DESCRIPTION

Provides additional information about the current C<NotificationHub>
status.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Reason => Str

An explanation for the current status.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Status => Str

Status information about the C<NotificationHub>.

=over

=item *

Values:

=over

=item *

C<ACTIVE>

=over

=item *

Incoming C<NotificationEvents> are replicated to this
C<NotificationHub>.

=back

=item *

C<REGISTERING>

=over

=item *

The C<NotificationConfiguration> is initializing. A
C<NotificationConfiguration> with this status can't be deregistered.

=back

=item *

C<DEREGISTERING>

=over

=item *

The C<NotificationConfiguration> is being deleted. You can't register
additional C<NotificationHubs> in the same Region as a
C<NotificationConfiguration> with this status.

=back

=back

=back




